      "title": "120,000 MT of Crude to reach SL soon",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Minister of Power and Energy Kanchana Wijesekara said that another vessel carrying 120,000 MT of crude oil is scheduled to reach the country in the near future.",
        "Accordingly, the Ministry said that the Sapugaskanda Oil Refinery will be able to be operate at full capacity for another 40 days.",
        "Sri Lanka Govt must permit the safe return of Gotabaya & Family \u2013 HRCSL"
